data.description: Price Improvement! A stunning 2019-built home boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 1 half bath. This property features a beautifully landscaped exterior, newly installed roof (June 2023) and extended patio in the backyard (March 2021). This home showcases an open floor plan that maximizes space and functionality, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout the home. The kitchen is a standout with quartz countertops and gorgeous backsplash that infuses the room with character and color.   As you step into the living room, you'll notice a built-in cabinet that adds both style and ample storage to the space.  In addition to its outstanding features, this property is situated in a desirable location with great schools nearby. The neighborhood also has a community pool to enjoy and is conveniently located near a shopping center and waterpark.   Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional home, where you can relish in the beauty of the nearby lake, explore the walking trail, and experience the comfort, style, and convenience it offers. Schedule a viewing today and transform this house into your dream home.
